The wind model presented here is to simulate the colliminated MHD disc-wind
 calculations of 
\begin_inset ERT
status Collapsed

\layout Standard

\backslash 
citealt{krasnopolsky:2003}
\end_inset 

 in small scale (
\begin_inset Formula $\sim10$
